node.text: #Pilots, this one's for you. The #G650ER comes complete with four adaptive LCD displays, synthetic vision, #EFVS for touchdown and rollout, dual standby multifunction controllers, a host of features that reduce pilot workload and so much more. #SoundOn for the #ArtOfExcellence.

node.text: The #G600 — exceeding your every expectation, in the cabin and flight deck alike. Experience class-leading speed and range, the most advanced technology and an unparalleled cabin experience. #ArtOfExcellence

node.text:
#NEWS: Gulfstream just became the first company to earn the National Aeronautic Association's new Sustainable Wings certification for roundtrip, record-setting flights using sustainable aviation fuel — this time in a #G500:

✈️Savannah to San Francisco: 548.80 mph (4 hours, 17 minutes)
✈️San Francisco to Savannah: 546.67 mph (4 hours, 18 minutes)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Gulfstream Aerospace on July 30, 2021. May be an image of airplane and outdoors.

node.text: Today's #FanFriday by @zachypoobaer features a #G700 landing in Savannah after a flight-test mission. #ArtOfExcellence
